Class Sqrt

    • jason.asSemantics.DefaultArithFunction

    ArithFunction, java.io.Serializable

    public class Sqrt
extends DefaultArithFunction

    Function: math.sqrt(N): encapsulates java Math.sqrt(N); returns the correctly rounded positive square root of N.

    Example:

    • math.sqrt(9): returns 3.
